
   *=============================================================*
                   Magical WEAPONS in Avenir Domain
   *=============================================================*

Shintor                      (~Avenir/common/bazaar/Obj/wield/shintor)
Creator:        Ilyian
Desc:           shimmering longsword
Stats:          normal 40/45; shimmering 50/50
Special:        Special damage type dependant on the alignment of the
                last creature slain with the sword
Magic:          Enchantment
Props:          OBJ_M_NO_BUY, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON
Cloned by:      Jadestone Doll (/d/Avenir/common/bazaar/NPCS/jadestone)
Where:          (~Avenir/common/bazaar/extr/hill)
Difficulty:     Quite difficult. Must defeat Jadestone Doll to get
                it, who, aside from being a very tough Npcs, heals
                and poisons.

Glimmering acid-etched blade     (~Avenir/common/dark/obj/tooth_knife)
Creator:        Boriska
Desc:           white tooth-knife
Stats           hit(35), pen(40)
Special:        
Magic:          Enchantment
Props:          OBJ_M_NO_BUY
Cloned by:      Can be made by player (miniquest)
Difficulty:     Requires tough monster to be killed in order to make it,
                requires certain item and skills to wield it.
                Chance of death, mana and fatigue penalties when
                trying to wield it.

Hallor                          (~Avenir/common/bazaar/infidel/obj/hallor)
Creator:        Cirion
Desc:           oaken cudgel
Stats:          hit(45), pen(49)
Special:        The club drains fatigue when it gets a good hit. If the
                enemy has resistances, there is a chance that the effect
                will be deflected back on to the wielder.
Magic:          Enchantment
Props:          OBJ_M_NO_BUY, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON
Cloned by:      Nochipa Silve (~Avenir/common/bazaar/infidel/mon/nochipa)
Where:          (~Avenir/common/bazaar/infidel/quar8)
Difficulty:     Quite difficult, requires difficult npc to be killed
                to get it, who heals herself and blinds players. 

Feather knife                (~Avenir/common/dark/obj/f_knife)
Creator:        Grace, June 1996
Desc:           irridescent rainbow-hued feather        
Stats:          hit(20), pen(40)
Special:        Has light of +2, is lightweight, and sharp.
                Light property fails after one hour.
Magic:          Fire, 75; Life, 25;
Props:          All required props, plus OBJ_I_LIGHT, 2
Cloned by:      (/d/Avenir/common/dark/mon/w_wolf) &
                (/d/Avenir/common/dark/l2/n5b)
Where:          (/d/Avenir/common/dark/l2/n5 & 5a)
Difficulty:     Should provide a challange to get for 'normal' players.
                The wolf has special healing ability, and 
                does serious damage with its bite, claws, and wing-tips.

Cwicseolfor     /d/Avenir/common/holm/obj/falchion.c   
Creator:        Lilith, January 1997
Desc:           basket-hilt falchion    
Stats:          hit(50) pen(46)
Special:        This is a Sword of Quickening, adds LIVE_I_QUICKNESS +55
Checks:         Checks for DEX, AWARENESS, and SWORD. Cannot be wielded 
                if gloves are worn or if intox > 50%. Mana and fatigue costs.
Magic:          enchantment
Props:          OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO,
                OBJ_M_NO_BUY, OBJ_S_WIZINFO
Cloned by:      /d/Avenir/common/holm/mon/noble
Where:          /d/Avenir/common/holm/*
Difficulty:     The npc is very hard to kill. 

Serpent Staff   /d/Avenir/common/holm/obj/serpent_staff.c
Creator:        Lilith 01/25/97
Desc:           serpentine staff
Stats:          WT polearm; hit(30) pen(25).
Special:        Transforms into a serpent when dropped.
Checks:         The serpent checks for Dex and animal handling using
                resolve_task formidable. Recharge time for transformation.
Magic:          enchantment
Props:          OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO,
Cloned by:      /d/Avenir/common/holm/mon/priest
Where:          /d/Avenir/common/holm/cave/*
Difficulty:     The npc which carries it would have a random 1 in 5
                chance of being cloned. It is a decent fighter.

Falcata         /d/Avenir/common/dead/obj/falcata.c
Creator:        Lilith, August 2001
Desc:           sybarun falcata
Stats:          hit (50)  pen (42)  Slash|Impale
Special:        Does MAGIC_DT to Enemies of Sybarus.
Checks:         STR, DIS & SWORD; cannot be more than 50% max intox, costs 
                fatigue to wield. Cannot be wielded by infidels.
Magic:          enchantment, death 
Props:          OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO,
                OBJ_M_NO_BUY,  OBJ_S_WIZINFO
Cloned by:      /d/Avenir/common/dead/mon/wight
Where:          /d/Avenir/common/dead/marsh/*
Difficulty:     This npc is a good fighter, a challenge to get to.

Khopesh         /d/Avenir/common/city/obj/wep/khopesh.c
Creator:        Lilith, July 2003
Desc:           sybarun khopesh
Stats:		    hit (45)   pen (46)  Slash
Special:        adds up to 20 levels of SS_WEP_SWORD, max 100.
Checks:         INT, DEX, SWORD; no infidels; intox must be <50%.
                Costs fatigue to wield and unwield.
Magic:		    enchantment  
Props:          OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO,
                OBJ_M_NO_BUY,  OBJ_S_WIZINFO, OBJ_M_NO_STEAL
Cloned by:      /d/Avenir/common/city/mon/dej-minah3.c 
Where:          /d/Avenir/common/city/entry/e1
Difficulty:     NPC is an excellent fighter. Access is restricted, player
                must obtain access to the City first.

Akram's Dagger  /d/Avenir/union/obj/akram_dagger
Creator:        Lilith Dec 2003
Desc:           <name>'s dagger  (knife)
Stats:          35  / 40; W_IMPALE & MAGIC_DT
Special:        Bonus to guild-specific skills & +10 to 2h combat, does
                damage attack to enemies of Sybarus (like falcata).
Magic:          transformation
Props:          OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO,etc
Cloned by:      /d/Avenir/union/npc/hephamenios
Where:          /d/Avenir/union/room/forge
Difficulty:     Union members only. Member must complete guru quest and 
                then the dagger quest.  Quest is repeatable to make the
                dagger again, as desired. Member must gather several items
                which can take a while, and then wait 30+ minutes while 
                NPC makes it. Not wieldable by non-members.

Kesoit Bow      /d/Avenir/common/bazaar/infidels/bj/kesoit_bow	
Creator:        Lilith, June 2004
Desc:           kesoit short bow
Stats:          Hit 43-47; Pen 42-47
Special:        Heals 30 - 60 fatigue every 15 minutes; adds quickness 50.
Checks:         Can't wield if intox > 50%
Magic:          Enchantment
Props:          OBJ_I_IS_MAGIC_WEAPON, MAGIC_AM_MAGIC, MAGIC_AM_ID_INFO,
Cloned by:      Nochipa /d/Avenir/common/bazaar/infidel/mon/nochipa
Where:          /d/Avenir/common/bazaar/infidel/quar8
Difficulty:     Quite difficult, requires difficult npc to be killed
                to get it, who heals herself and blinds players, and
                clones air spirits to help her. 
               

